summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Davis Addition to the City of Seattle; first addition to Lake Forest Park; Park View Tracts; southeast quarter of Section 17, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Northeast Quarter of Section 25, Township 23 North, Range 3 East; Lake Washington Shorelands; Patrick Linda Addition; Jersey Summer Home Tracts; and Government Lot 3, Section 34, Township 24 North Range East.
